    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在Aven Colony为人类建造一个新的家园。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索主Aven Prime—一个距离地球几光年之远的满是沙漠，苔原和湿地的星球。在Aven Colony，你负责人类的第一次太阳系外的定居。在那里，你要修建小殖民地，并将其扩张成庞大的都市，同时，你还要处理在一个新世界定居时所会面临的各种挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修建殖民地里的基础设施，关注市民们的福利和幸福，管理好资源，并带领你的殖民地在主Aven Prime—这个残酷并时常危险的现实环境里走向繁荣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特征：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在一个外星世界建立殖民地：</strong>为人类在一个新世界里建造新的家园。那个世界里有着低氧大气层、极端电风暴、碎片风暴、沙尘暴和会喷发出致命毒气的地热喷口，并且那里的一天如此之长，它们甚至有自己的季节。从茂密的湿地环境到更难以居住的沙漠和北极，探索多种生物群落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ea2b95c867d5fca89738e95ced193f2c.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ea2b95c867d5fca89738e95ced193f2c.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ea2b95c867d5fca89738e95ced193f2c.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遇见当地居民：</strong>遇见各种外星生命体，包括巨大的沙虫，致命的瘟疫孢子和一种被称为&quot;The Creep&quot;的邪恶真菌感染体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/8579e6f6ab9c0d9a3d70114fe8db7078.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/8579e6f6ab9c0d9a3d70114fe8db7078.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/8579e6f6ab9c0d9a3d70114fe8db7078.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理你的殖民地居民：</strong>在一个新世界里定居不是一件简单的事情。作为一个新殖民地的总督，你将要加班加点地为你的居民处理各种新环境问题。通过使用12种不同的“叠加”模式，你可以管理殖民地里的作物、居民、幸福度、犯罪率、空气、电力、就业、资源、交通、结构、无人机和水。赢得殖民地居民们的尊重，从殖民地总督晋升为远征地总统！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/449bac5bddfa3a39b900a3e79b8501da.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/449bac5bddfa3a39b900a3e79b8501da.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/449bac5bddfa3a39b900a3e79b8501da.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索过去：</strong>主艾文里有着很多秘密。玩一个完整的单人战役，并参与到揭露这个新世界的许多秘密的故事中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/3e7e5661fab6bbf39488490ac6944b01.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/3e7e5661fab6bbf39488490ac6944b01.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/3e7e5661fab6bbf39488490ac6944b01.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>构建未来：</strong>使用建筑无人机来建造各种结构的建筑物来供居民们居住，建立贸易线路，并欢迎更多的移民们前来定居！通过一些升级层来增强现有建筑物的属性，将你的殖民地推到新高度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/20bebc0f085bcaf3680becbe01e0c192.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/20bebc0f085bcaf3680becbe01e0c192.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/20bebc0f085bcaf3680becbe01e0c192.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>远征系统：</strong>部署你的先锋精锐团队去探索外星遗迹，修复文物，修理失事船只并营救迷路的探险者。准备好采取对瘟疫和蠕孢窝的对策，同时抵御分裂组织，叛军和威胁到你们新文明的主艾文残留机器人守卫军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/92abe3f0b93b3fd478d32f36df7cf60f.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/92abe3f0b93b3fd478d32f36df7cf60f.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/92abe3f0b93b3fd478d32f36df7cf60f.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>过冬准备：</strong>一个功能齐全的日╱夜和季节循环。冬天，主艾文会冻结成冰——农场不能种植作物，太阳能电池板也会产生更少的电量。采取措施来熬过这恶劣的气候！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ec69384891d407897bf91e95268bea22.poster.avif?t=1761829468\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ec69384891d407897bf91e95268bea22.webm?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484900/extras/ec69384891d407897bf91e95268bea22.mp4?t=1761829468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
